									<p>Initials written in larger characters.</p>
									<p>Catchwords on every verso.</p>
									<p>Last line written within the ruling.</p>
									<p>Some marginal notes in semi-cursive and cursive script, mostly marked by a simple pen and ink design.</p>
								</layout>
